scenes.description: Vestia Zeta performs a 'Cat Dance' challenge with other Hololive members and takes a 'Zetamin' boost.
Kureiji Ollie challenges Zeta to perform a cool secret agent pose with her gun.
Watson Amelia challenges Zeta to balance a 'Zetamin' container on her head while standing on one foot.
Zeta thanks her guests and prepares to announce new merchandise.
Announcement of the holoh3ro Card Case - Vestia Zeta merchandise.
